reviewText: I purchased this for my grown son as a Christmas present. He loves this dvd.
COULDN'T FINISH THE MOVIE TOSSED IT OUT AFTER A FEW MINUTES DISGUSTING

this Asian horror movie from the 1980s is indicative of how good Asian horror movies were. in todays world of Asian PG13 movies you can see how horror movies have changed for the worst.corpse mania is not all gore but a wonderful display color and a sound script and story line.at this price it well worth buying.
